Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.98,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:08.11,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first of September... \NWhy are the mornings still so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.07,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to finish yesterday's curry, fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.12,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.25,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:22.66,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.21,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.46,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,How you been, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.13,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.25,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finish your summer homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:30.71,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you brush your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:31.96,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:35.55,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.55,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:40.89,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must've had an eventful vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:42.68,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break's in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.44,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,We're living in the second term now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.86,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,On to a new stage in the Culture Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:49.27,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,To find something new—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.53,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to have something\Nhappen over summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.19,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Yuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:55.99,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,But sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.24,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Of course something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.20,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it was your seventeenth summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:03.91,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Completely different from the summer\Nof a single woman who's hit thirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.80,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,- Indeed, the world can be so cruel...\N- I guess nothing special happened for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre! Preparation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.47,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,pure pureparato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be very strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.35,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,tsuyoku nanka naikedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre! Pre-parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.56,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,pure pureparedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:27.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm gonna catch you\None of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:27.19,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka kimiwo tsukamaeru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:32.23,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,pu re purepa pu re purepa pu re purepa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:33.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Cracking and crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:33.57,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,warete baribari
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:38.16,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,pu re purepa pu re purepa pu re purepa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:45.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your guard down and expect\Na poking attack from my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:45.45,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,yudan shitara sono yubi\Nchiku chiku atakku kakugo shite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:51.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be small, but I can still\Npluck you like a flea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:51.13,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,chiisai kedo hasamuno\Nmijinko mitai na anata
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:57.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm longing for a plastic heart.\N(Plus, plus, somehow a minus)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:57.68,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hoshiinowa purasuchikkuna haato\N(purasu purasu dakedo mainasu)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:04.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who realizes how\Nboring that'd be will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:04.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,demo soreja tsumaranai\Nsokoni kizuita monogachi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is so bittersweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.60,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,koiwa amakute nigaimono
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:13.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Plain and simple while\Ncomplicated and mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:13.73,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,tanjun meikai hukuzatsu kaikina shiromono
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You get worried about\Nthe most pointless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.78,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,doudemoii kotobakkari\Nkinishitari suruno
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel? THAT's how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.66,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,donna kanji sonna kanji
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You are gentle and\Nsincere yet eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.78,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,onkou tokujitsu\Nekisentorikku na anata
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I act tough as we butt heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.83,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,tsuyogaru soburiwo\Nzenshin matotte tachiuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I get dizzy whenever I try\Nto be honest to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.66,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sunaona dakedato shigekigai\Ntsuyokute kurakura
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:34.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I get hurt. You get hurt.\NInnocent preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:34.80,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kizutsui chauno kizutsuke chauno\Njunjou pureparato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:40.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,In my mind, I'm always alone\Non an innocent Pre-Parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:40.68,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,atamano nakawa itsumo hitorino\Njunjou pureparedo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:51.27,ImagetextBD,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ohashi High School Culture Festival\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:51.27,DefaultBD,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So, once again, they're limiting\Nthe festival to one day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.32,DefaultBD,Murase,0000,0000,0000,,The president's influence wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.94,DefaultBD,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't a unilateral decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.03,DefaultBD,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,We made a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.03,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is ours!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.03,DefaultBD,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiations with the faculty are underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.74,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.90,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes as planned, surrendering a second
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,day of festivities will be more than worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:14.04,DefaultBD,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do whatever it takes to make\Nthis year's Culture Festival a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:20.01,DefaultBD,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my last major\Nschool event, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.77,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then next time, let's look for UFOs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:33.73,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:34.69,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.86,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, slowtard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.07,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:41.15,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't touch the ball.\NMy nails are too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.57,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Might break one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.91,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.12,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that cute smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.20,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan is an angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.95,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Palm-top Tiger fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.04,DefaultBD,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take Kashii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.87,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say Kihara's definitely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.83,DefaultBD,E,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Ami-chan's riding the tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.75,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.58,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to ride me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.13,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and zentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.84,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.89,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any ladies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.14,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,And what the hell does "zentle" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:10.81,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you fellas interested in\Nseeing the girls you pine for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,looking cute in a non-everyday way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.65,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You feeling okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.48,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you got into some\Nweird hobby over summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.57,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.61,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,The Culture Festival is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.54,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,And during tomorrow's long homeroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:30.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,our class will decide what\Nwe'll be doing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.41,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.37,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the Culture Festival committee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.08,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.58,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:43.51,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,If we choose to go with a maid cafe, we'll\Nget to see the girls dressed as maids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:48.18,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,If the guys unite and force a vote,\Nwe'll have an indisputable majority!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.39,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,How's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.47,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.85,DefaultBD,D,0000,0000,0000,,Especially coming from Haruta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.98,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.27,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd replace the maid outfits...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.52,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,with cheongsam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.40,DefaultBD,D,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.07,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,I can picture that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.32,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, you with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.81,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.38,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I basically get to see her in\Na maid outfit at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.73,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A skintight cheongsam\Nwould be much more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.17,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.17,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too tight, I'll have to\Nmake her bra-pads again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.51,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,What are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.80,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.51,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd replace cheongsam with, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.47,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Lolita dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.58,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.27,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.89,DefaultBD,D,0000,0000,0000,,I want nurse uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.27,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,How do stewardess outfits sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.52,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass! They're called flight attendants!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.07,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't forget shrine maidens!\N- Hold up, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.73,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get off topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.20,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what were we even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.20,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A cosplay cafe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:51.08,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,is the perfect solution, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.87,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Boys' Locker Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.87,DefaultBD,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.25,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.21,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.55,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.39,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.93,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.26,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.93,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-chi tore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.35,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.23,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not slander my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:23.69,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You tripped over yourself and tore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.36,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for dodging that ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.11,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I already said that my nails are—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.03,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.64,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll mend the tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.58,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, spoiling her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.57,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure it's fixed by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:40.96,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.34,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you shift the blame\Nonto me and walk away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:43.92,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.99,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,They're so spunky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.38,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.72,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we should head back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.76,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.14,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.64,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,B-By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.06,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The thing you said about UFOs—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:03.48,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, instant noodles are truly\Nthe enemy of Diet Warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.69,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.23,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Absit omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.99,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to patch this with\Nanother piece of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:17.29,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll sacrifice one of\NYasuko's old long johns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.24,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.17,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.88,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that stupid bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.47,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.18,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.01,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Your phone's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.35,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,- Make it sto—\N- Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.68,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.18,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I said to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.48,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The man gets remarried and\Ndecides I don't belong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.77,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,so he gives me an apartment\Nand throws me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.77,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He abandoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.03,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely heartless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.24,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about your dad!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.61,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No, a stupid bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.53,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,He's still your father, no\Nmatter how awful he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.87,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Stupid bastard" is a bit much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.50,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,With family, you're always connected in\Nyour hearts, even when you're apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.46,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Like, you know—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.65,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I said he's a stupid bastard, and that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.09,DefaultBD,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,Stu-pid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.76,DefaultBD,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,Pid! Pid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.27,DefaultBD,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,- Stupid bas! Pid tard! Pid pi—\N- You don't need to learn that phrase!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.80,DefaultBD,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,Piles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.10,DefaultBD,Inko,0000,0000,15,,- Piles! P-Piles!\N- Inko-chan, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.14,DefaultBD,Inko,0000,0000,0000,,- P-P-Piles!\N- Oh? Talking about your daddy, Ryu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.35,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,- No way!\N- He was so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.14,DefaultBD,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,He kept magazines tucked under his shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.98,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,That story again!? That's not wonderful at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.44,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,And don't go blabbing that to other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.07,DefaultBD,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.53,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.49,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,We need to decide on a class exhibit, and\Nchoose a candidate for the pageant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.49,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,15,,Topic\NCulture Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:44.33,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Culture Festival Committee Member\NHaruta Koji
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:44.33,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, for the pageant, we'll go with\NAmi-chan, since I doubt anybo—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.21,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.25,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto\NKawashima Ami
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.25,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:57.89,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought, but I'm the\Npageant MC, so I can't be a participant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.56,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,However, I believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.27,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san would be a perfect choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.31,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.60,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,She's so little and cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.77,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,And she's well-known around school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.52,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What are you babbling about, Dumb-chi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.82,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to deal with that hassle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.65,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but that actually might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.12,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,The tiger certainly is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.83,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,I can see this workin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.33,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid jerks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.45,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.91,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do, Taiga-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.33,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of this class too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.71,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,so you should actively participate in such events.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.71,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.98,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't going to listen to me,\NI'll crush the whole damn festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:36.88,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.43,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it in. Hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.43,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You might actually win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.39,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.85,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.40,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Tiger will be our pageant candidate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:54.49,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on to what our class\Nwill do for the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.28,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.66,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Noto-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.07,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,How does a cosplay cafe sound!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.66,DefaultBD,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.24,DefaultBD,Maya,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that super lame?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.08,DefaultBD,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee some other\Nclass will do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:11.63,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm totally against it!\N- Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.34,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Just my two cents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.67,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I personally want to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.38,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Can't stand it, myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.64,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But I wouldn't mind if everyone\Nmanages to have fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.18,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.02,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,A h-haunted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.48,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Got a nosebleed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:29.98,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.40,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to say anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.03,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Just that a h-haunted house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.03,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.78,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.86,DefaultBD,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.86,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.95,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,So not gonna let it happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.37,DefaultBD,D,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.58,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Cafe? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.45,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Form a band and put on a concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.75,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck. Worst thing you could\Ndo in Japan right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.54,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That excitement won't last longer\Nthan a day! It's an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.50,DefaultBD,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all fall apart by Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.84,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's she ranting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:57.26,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,Something bad happen to her over summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.47,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're not getting anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.68,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just put it to a vote!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.97,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,- Write down your idea on a piece of paper!\N- Now we're voting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.60,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Won't matter what the girls write.\NThey're a disorganized mess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.40,DefaultBD,Noto,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They stand no chance against\Na united male front!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.02,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Okey-doke! Everybody done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.15,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.57,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.69,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.11,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.11,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! A draw!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.41,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Announcement time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.33,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,This year, our class will be\Nputting on a pro wrestling—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:31.46,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Who actually wrote down\N"pro wrestling show (no holds barred)"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.54,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.54,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.80,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go with majority rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.88,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.76,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Dumb-chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.68,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat her into all kinds of hells when\Nshe passes through Samsara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.14,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up and enjoy\Na class event, for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.88,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You need to open your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.61,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break. That, coming from\Nthe guy who's suddenly all excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.53,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Excited? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.97,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we came back from the trip—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:03.24,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.28,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:04.99,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.03,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It won't let me withdraw money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:08.08,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The balance is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.91,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.31,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.22,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I've been ignoring his calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.09,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how he reacts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.80,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.09,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Calls? Like the one the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.70,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He's called a bunch of times recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.88,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But I ignored them all because\Nthey pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.50,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's emptied out the account\Nfor my living expenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.77,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.24,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:37.70,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't say that about your parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.07,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call\NStupid Bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.74,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He's threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.28,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Just pick up, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:49.52,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will change if you don't talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:50.95,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.79,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in trouble without the money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.83,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.92,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She picked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.96,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why am I meeting with him by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.36,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.05,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.01,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying my daughter isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.68,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.43,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.16,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I've dug myself\Ninto an even deeper hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.02,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.02,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Takasu-kun, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.90,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well order whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.70,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah. No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.28,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having dinner in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.99,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,E-Er, I mean, I'll take you up on your offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.08,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,An egg bagel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.25,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.12,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.54,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Can we order?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.96,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,An egg bagel for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.88,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And I guess I'll have this salmon bagel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.88,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,With lots of cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.38,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,As much as you can fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.01,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.89,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, before I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.14,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.26,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.93,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I had something important to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.89,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:02.73,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... So are you and Taiga, y'know...dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.36,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.90,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, we're just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.03,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing romantic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:12.22,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,We just happen to be neighbors, and we\Nsomehow managed to hit it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.99,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.91,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Taiga must have\Ntold you about our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.79,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I remarried someone significantly\Nyounger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.84,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga had a hard time adjusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:28.51,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And that led to misunderstanding\Nafter misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.85,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,My new wife, her name is Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.14,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It got to the point where either\NTaiga or Yu had to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.14,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.73,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to live with Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.56,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The way we did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.29,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I came here to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.28,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No mistakes this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.07,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start over with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.82,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yu and I will be separating soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.69,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to live with Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.29,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.75,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Since I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.50,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is big.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:03.17,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your dad's come back for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.76,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.84,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Do a better job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.05,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Rinse for longer than five seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:11.22,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.72,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:18.02,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I promised to wash the dishes in return\Nfor you meeting with that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.77,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then do a better job!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.02,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.15,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.78,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.45,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't act like a typical grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.78,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.12,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Go boil water and make tea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:38.59,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.25,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he wants to live with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.04,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.54,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:48.38,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wants to live with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.63,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,And he asked me to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.93,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.76,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't meddle in someone\Nelse's family issues!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.14,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who sent me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.02,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,So you take the money, and that's the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.02,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.40,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm washing the dishes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.11,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's settled now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.86,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.78,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.03,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:10.57,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Face—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.36,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.24,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.28,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad was depressed\Nabout you ignoring him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.99,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I felt bad for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.04,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel bad for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.59,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.59,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.34,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.68,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,I felt responsible for what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.68,ImagetextBD,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,The Pro Wrestling Show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.51,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,so I made this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.18,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,A script for a wrestling show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.23,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't we drop this idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:42.94,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.73,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:47.48,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show some interest!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.11,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.74,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan already approved\Nand submitted our proposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.78,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:57.16,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,This might be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.24,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been assigned a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.54,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun, this is much\Nbetter than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.79,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.29,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda feel like celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.17,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.71,DefaultBD,GirlA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.80,DefaultBD,GirlB,0000,0000,0000,,This is really well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.92,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun, let's do the best we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.68,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's start rehearsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.05,DefaultBD,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.39,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,In the near future,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:24.77,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,the students of 2-C are living happily in\Npeace under their leader, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.98,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.23,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,There were those who found\Nthis peace offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:32.99,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,The Palm-top Tiger—evil incarnate—and her\Nunderling, Takasu Ryuji the delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.94,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:37.82,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I her underling?\NAnd a delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.95,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I evil incarnate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:43.54,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,No questions. Just hear me out, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.58,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,The Palm-top Tiger attacks\Nthe members of 2-C!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.46,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,They are brainwashed one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.21,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,But! Ami-chan's furious efforts set them free,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.59,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone joins together in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:55.63,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,successfully driving the Palm-top Tiger\Nand badboy Takasu Ryuji away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.30,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,And then they live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:17:59.76,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:02.18,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we get\Nfor hearing you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.39,DefaultBD,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,But it's simple and dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.31,DefaultBD,Nana,0000,0000,0000,,This might turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.14,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.06,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.07,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... You're so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:13.78,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.99,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,First the pageant, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.16,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so intent on making\Nme do these weird things!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:21.45,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,If hitting me will make you feel\Nbetter, go right on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.87,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,All right! That's what I'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.00,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But violence is not the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.96,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the Palm-top Tiger's really into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.79,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,Rehearsing already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.84,DefaultBD,C,0000,0000,0000,,That was so intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.80,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.59,DefaultBD,Haruta,0000,0000,0000,,Now, deliver the tiger's brainwashing line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.63,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Say your line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.59,DefaultBD,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Look, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.55,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The tiger appears, shouting incoherently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.05,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Amin's changed lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.56,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.14,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:46.89,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.52,DefaultBD,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun said he had a special\Nrole for me to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.02,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.73,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,The school just rendered their decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.15,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,This year's Culture Festival\Nwill be a class competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.03,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,The first-place class will receive\Nan extravagant prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.28,DefaultBD,All,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.78,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,I should mention the prizes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.70,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Option one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.58,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,A refrigerator in your classroom\Nfor the rest of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.75,DefaultBD,Maya,0000,0000,0000,,Love that chilled juice, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.67,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Option two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:17.38,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,The classroom gets one of next year's primo\Nair conditioners installed {\i1}this{\i0} month!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.26,DefaultBD,A,0000,0000,0000,,Love that moist air, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.30,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,The ban on electrical devices\Nin the restroom will be lifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.56,DefaultBD,B,0000,0000,0000,,Love to curl your hair, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:26.97,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.48,DefaultBD,Kitamura,0000,0000,0000,,Coupons from Supermarket Kanoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.81,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Love those coupons, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.86,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.07,DefaultBD,Maya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The guys need to pull their weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.32,DefaultBD,All,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:43.24,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.20,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Amberjack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.41,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Prepared how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.45,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Teri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.16,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yaki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.75,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.21,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you\Nhere...this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.05,DefaultBD,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.85,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damn stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.64,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.90,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.15,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, you stupid mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.82,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And stop taking his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:17.82,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.53,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be the one\Nperson on {\i1}my{\i0} side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.66,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying this {\i1}because{\i0} I'm on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.45,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,This is for your own good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.57,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.91,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.70,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't he come for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.20,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You could at least hear him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:30.79,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.41,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.50,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.25,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.29,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.05,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you crying about being abandoned!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.47,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.84,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest with yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.30,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go home, don't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.26,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.77,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.31,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.48,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I abandoned him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.48,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Tossed him like a pile of worthless trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.44,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.36,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:02.95,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really see him as trash!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:06.78,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,My old man's never coming home,\Nno matter how much I beg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.12,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't for Taiga's own good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.29,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:14.00,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.00,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:19.67,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.84,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.55,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:24.80,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Get that look off your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.88,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,Tai—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.22,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:31.64,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I'll try to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.44,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't know if I'll be\Nable to change how I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.31,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's what you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.65,DefaultBD,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.45,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a good thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.33,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...a good thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.00,DefaultBD,Ryuji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Add vanilla salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:58.71,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,banira sorutode
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning love.
